One of the best locations to get a great shot of the Eiffel Tower or have an impromptu photo op is Pont de Bir-Hakeim or the France Reborn Statue!  The Bridge its self is an iconic Paris landmark that has been the backdrop of several movies! With the Tour Eiffel in the background it‚Äôs a great place to take photos and portraits! I do recommend going early, as with any place in Paris where you may want to have less crowds for photos!  Pont de Bir-Hakeim is also very popular with some of Paris‚Äô local photographers, so if you set up a professional shoot, odds are you‚Äôll end up at this place as well!
